criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  PCR for SARS-CoV 2 positive on NPS swab or high suspicion of SARS-CoV 2 with ongoing
             swab;

          -  All ages;

          -  All genders;

          -  Informed consent obtained.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Failure to obtain the informed consent.
